txt.en: Lord Celeborn and Lady Galadriel have devised a daring plan: to cross the river Anduin and attack the fortress of Dol Guldur in the depths of Mirkwood.
It is time to execute Lord Celeborn's daring plan: an attack upon the fortress of Dol Guldur, in the depths of Southern Mirkwood.
